1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:22,000
Being a dog is a little annoying.

2
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:39,000
Food you don't like and people always trying to hug you.

3
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:43,000
So what do I do?

4
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:45,000
Simple.

5
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:57,000
You can always ignore those people and hide for as long as you can.

6
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:09,000
And when the door is open just go out and take a moment for yourself.

7
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:21,000
Smell around, explore the ground, clean up your mess and just chill.

8
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:27,000
Enjoy your kingdom.

9
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:37,000
It will not hurt you if you just sit down and think about life.

10
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:48,000
Before you go inside and get humiliated all over again.

11
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:55,000
But you can always find a place inside and enjoy the affection of the giants.

12
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:58,000
Just relax.

13
00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:08,000
It's never too late for living a wonderful life.


